Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.25,0:47:23.59,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With his final defi~ance
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.00,0:47:27.86,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The empire was all swept away
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.35,0:47:32.78,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Their spirits were drained, as his own soul was stained
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.04,0:47:37.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And suffer together his fate
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.40,0:47:41.36,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To lie in wait
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.62,0:47:46.01,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Outside time, far behind shadow’s veil
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.50,0:47:50.74,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For in their return, deep within they will yearn
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.96,0:47:56.59,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That their crystal hearts may prevail
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.35,0:48:31.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Heavy is the crown she wears
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.14,0:48:35.59,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Knowing the cost, the sadness she bears
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.93,0:48:46.35,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Left to ache while weeping for his fate~~
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.82,0:48:52.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Perhaps one day
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.25,0:48:58.28,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The shadow will be sent away
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.95,0:49:04.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,When light will have won, maybe there in the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.69,0:49:09.90,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The king will revive in its rays
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.60,0:49:16.28,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,One thing's for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.62,0:49:21.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As the ages move on
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.82,0:49:25.57,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The harshest of debts is to live with regret
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.99,0:49:27.82,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,So chase what you love
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.97,0:49:40.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And fight on for the one that you lost…